description:
A standard, army-issue sword. The insignia of the 
royal family is on the hilt.
name: Army Sword

description:
A standard, army-issue axe. The handle is worn down 
from years of hard training.
name: Army Axe

description:
A steel longsword. It’s so sharp that it could shred 
paper, but don’t do that. It’ll ruin the blade.
name: Longsword

description:
A sword used by pirates and sailors. Extremely light-
weight, which makes it difficult to use.
name: Cutlass

description:
A sword made up of many smaller blades, allowing the 
blade to move like a snake. It has a higher hit rate.
name: Snake Sword

description:
A sword whose hilt and blade shines in many colours 
under the light. Allows you to use a special skill!
name: Dragon Slayer

description:
A sword resembling that of ancient warriors. Has a 
chance of stunning or weakening enemies with each blow.
name: Gladius

description:
For the edgelord in all of us. It’s larger and sharper 
than what farmers use.
name: Battle Scythe

description:
An axe with an additional pointy end. The longer range 
increases critical hit rates, but slows movement.
name: Poleaxe

description:
A mace with a silver ball, which gives the weapon its 
name. Has a tiny chance of stunning enemies.
name: Full Moon

description:
Placing a hand on the blade of this axe will give the 
feeling of a beating heart. Drains HP from enemies.
name: Vampyr

description:
Not an executioner, an executor. Meaning one who 
does, and makes a change. Unlocks a special skill!
name: Executor

description:
A giant drumstick. What chicken made this? An extremely 
powerful axe, nonetheless. Nintucky... fried chicken!!!
name: Fried Drumstick

description:
Only the longest and skinniest shoestring fry can be 
made into a katana like this. Ninja... fry!!!
name: Shoestring Fry

description:
A lance from Captain Risky. Attacks with ice, fire and 
lightning ALL AT THE SAME TIME! (Not a lie)
name: Risky Bardiche

description:
A bow named after the grace of Goddess Ninlil. A light 
breeze blows behind the wielder, helping their arrow.
name: Goddess Footsteps

description:
Quick, fast and sloppy. The pain invigorates enemies 
for some reason. Fran isn’t allowed to touch it.
name: Garter’s Belt
